Package: vault
Type: Package
Title: Allows a user to interact with HashiCorp Vault
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ben", "Gonzalez", , "gonzalezben393@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0008-6307-5161")))
Maintainer: Ben Gonzalez<gonzalezben393@gmail.com>
Description: This package allows HashiCorp Vault users to interact with  their Vault instance via its built in API.The user simply needs a token from their Vault instance to interact with it. Utilizing the token users can read & write secrets to and from vault via the specified path e.g.(secrets/path).
URL: https://github.com/gonzalezben81/vault
BugReports: https://github.com/gonzalezben81/vault/issues
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: httr, jsonlite
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    httptest
VignetteBuilder: knitr
